text:
I remember needing to have three
different versions of the HP "Universal" driver because none of them supported
the range of all the HP printers we had, and assigning the "wrong" one would
either print gibberish or disallow critical features for some models. On
Tuesday, February 6, 2024 at 18:27, Philip Elder eloquently inscribed:
Link: None
